# Project Structure

## Core Components

- [src/server.js](mdc:src/server.js) - Main Express server setup and entry point
- [src/scrapers/](mdc:src/scrapers/) - Contains scraper implementations 
- [src/routes/](mdc:src/routes/) - API endpoints and request handling
- [src/utils/](mdc:src/utils/) - Utility functions and storage management

## Scraper Components

- [src/scrapers/invaluable/](mdc:src/scrapers/invaluable/) - Main scraper implementation for Invaluable
- [src/scrapers/artist-directory-scraper.js](mdc:src/scrapers/artist-directory-scraper.js) - Artist directory scraper

## API Routes

- [src/routes/search.js](mdc:src/routes/search.js) - Main search endpoint with options
- [src/routes/scraper.js](mdc:src/routes/scraper.js) - Scraper job management
- [src/routes/general-scraper.js](mdc:src/routes/general-scraper.js) - General scraping endpoints

## Utility Components

- [src/utils/search-storage.js](mdc:src/utils/search-storage.js) - Storage service for search results
- [src/utils/storage-manager.js](mdc:src/utils/storage-manager.js) - Storage management utilities

## Automation Scripts

- [scripts/](mdc:scripts/) - Contains various automation scripts
- [*.sh files](mdc:run_with_delay.sh) - Shell scripts for running scrapers with different parameters
